    "chunk_id": "docling_docstructbench_llm-raw-scihub-o.O-chem.200700118.pdf_7_10",
    "text": "Scheme 2 summarizes these photochemical events. In addition, there are secondary reactions involving, for example, the elimination of OCS, together presumably with CH,F although this could not be detected, as well as the formation of loosely bound CO complexes.",
